comment_data.body:
Instead of using `with`, which isn't a [very encouraged practice](https://nix.dev/guides/best-practices#with-scopes), use `builtin.attrValues` with `inherit`

For example
```nix
devShell = pkgs.mkShell {
  packages = builtin.attrValues {
    inherit (pkgs)
     stylua
     luaPackages.luacheck
     ...
     ;
  };
};
```

Also `packages` should be used over `buildInputs`, another nitpick of mine is that we can drop the `flake-utils` input entirely in favor of using `genAttrs` which provides a cleaner, readable Flake. Read this for more on that https://ayats.org/blog/no-flake-utils

